### 2C. Reading Progress Indicator

**New file: `client/src/components/ReadingProgress/ReadingProgress.jsx`** + **`ReadingProgress.css`**

A thin bar at the top of the viewport (position: fixed, top: 0) showing scroll progress through the article content in `ContentView.jsx`. Uses `requestAnimationFrame` + scroll listener to compute `scrollTop / (scrollHeight - clientHeight)`. Amber gradient fill matching the accent.

