|-------|------|--------|--------|-------------|
| 1A | Design Tokens | 0.5 day | Medium | None |
| 1B | Toast System | 1.5 days | **High** | None |
| 2A | Skeleton Loaders | 0.5 day | **High** | None |
| 2B | Empty States | 0.5 day | Medium | None |
| 2C | Reading Progress | 0.5 day | Medium | None |
| 2D | Page Transitions | 0.5 day | Medium | None |
| 3A | Button Press | 0.25 day | Medium | 1A (tokens) |
