| 4A | Skip-to-content | 0.25 day | Low | 1A (tokens) |
| 4B | Focus Rings | 0.25 day | Medium | 1A (tokens) |
| 4C | Reduced Motion | 0.5 day | Medium | None |
| 4D | Aria Labels | 0.5 day | Medium | None |
