**Recommended build order:** 1A -> 1B -> 2A -> 4B -> 4C -> 2D -> 3A-F -> 2B -> 2C -> 4A -> 4D -> 4E

This order front-loads the two highest-impact items (toast system + skeleton loaders), establishes the token foundation early, and weaves accessibility into the process rather than leaving it last.

